# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Teacher Copilot — environment configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and add your Anthropic API key.
#
# WITHOUT a key, the app still runs in DEMO MODE with realistic
# pre-written content — perfect for a safe live demo.
# WITH a key, all features use real Claude AI generation.

# Your Anthropic API key (get one at https://console.anthropic.com)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model.
# Default is claude-opus-4-8 (highest quality).
# For a faster live demo you can use: claude-haiku-4-5
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
